Class GameObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.a3.maze.GameObject
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Actor, Tile, Treasure

    public abstract class GameObject
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    General abstract class that every object in the game should have, handles rendering, positioning and the listener system
    Author:
    Tim - Creator, Mike - Contributor
